1) install the latest versions of nodejs and npm

3) run the following commands in separate terminals, from this directory:
gulp
node static-server

If running from VM, when browser-syncing w/ phone, need to activate bridge mode on the VM, instead of NAT. See: http://stackoverflow.com/questions/3244650/windows-xp-exposing-websites-in-iis-in-local-network

